casebody.data:
Oriana CAMPOS, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
GREEN TREE SERVICING, LLC, et al., Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-4418 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. May 23, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Appellee Green Tree Servicing, LLC's motion to dismiss is granted, and this appeal is dismissed for failure to prosecute.

NORTHCUTT, SALARIO, and BADALAMENTI, JJ., Concur.
